HEADWORD: Amomum
<hw>A*mo"mum</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., fr. Gr.
<?/ an Indian spice plant.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A genus of
